  * Ganglia Web Frontend conflicting license for Templating class
    http://www.mail-archive.com/ganglia-developers@lists.sourceforge.net/msg04072.html
    bnicholes: I don't consider this to be a showstopper since it is not a
               regression from previously released versions of Ganglia.
               We should get this fixed in order to resolve any licensing 
               conflicts in the web front end, but the affects are no worse
               than any previously released code.

